name: Tween3D
shortDescription: Smoothly squash, strentch, tint and wobble 3D models.
description: Change 3D models proportions over time to make smooth animations like wobbling.
- The Tween behavior is now required by the 3D Tween behavior. Add the Tween behavior on any object that uses the 3D Tween behavior
